#### PR description:

 There are some trigger paths which are not available with enough events. An example: like TTbar sample does not have genuine photons so Higgs to diphoton samples might be useful. Following the past strategy with all four samples to be available now for HLT validation. Please follow additional inoformation in this Jira. 
**https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/PDMVRELVALS-115**
